summary:
No material trading or capital markets information identified in this announcement.  

### Summary (Non-Trading/Capital Markets Impact):
- **Event Participation**: Company representatives will present at the AIG Victorian Minerals Round-up 2025 on geological modeling techniques at the Sunday Creek Gold-Antimony Project.  
- **Project Highlights**:  
  - High-grade intercepts (66 >100 g/t AuEq, 73 >50–100 g/t AuEq) reported at Sunday Creek.  
  - Antimony exposure (21–24% of in-situ value) highlighted as strategically significant due to China’s export restrictions.  
  - US tariff exemption for antimony ores noted.  

**Note**: This is an operational/technical update without direct capital markets implications (e.g., no financing, M&A, or material asset changes). Focus remains on exploration progress and metallurgical insights.
